<section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>The <code>data-toggle-tags</code> attribute transforms a fieldset of checkboxes into selectable pill-shaped tags. The styling is pure CSS via <code>:has(:checked)</code> &mdash; JavaScript is only loaded when you need a max selection limit via <code>data-max</code>.</p>

